Package com.laundry.laundryMgmt.records

Record Class MachineRecord

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
com.laundry.laundryMgmt.records.MachineRecord
Record Components:
machineId - unique identifier for the laundry machine.
name - name or identifier of the machine.
available - the status of the machine
machineStatus - the current status or condition of the machine (operational, out of order).
progress - the current progress or state of a running cycle
cycleType - type of cycle the machine
startingTime - the time when the machine's cycle started or is scheduled to start.
public record MachineRecord(long machineId, String name, boolean available, boolean machineStatus, int progress, CycleType cycleType, LocalTime startingTime) extends Record
Version:
1.0 Represents a machine record used in laundry management.
Author:
David PETREL
